    <Label name="lblTips14" id="19965aa2-60b7-43d4-aa02-a88ce36f6a79">
        <caption>When in discharge colour coding mode, select some slots to colour. Hold the ALT key down and select the same number of slots. When you click the Discharge colour coding button the colour coding is painted for both the discharge and the load.

The slots selected whilst the ALT key are pressed are the load locations. Clicking SOB or DLR also draws the opposite action. Once linked job and planning for the load part are automatic, but are configurable and can be amended.
</caption>
